clinic.name: Laurelhurst Family Dentistry
clinic.description:
We Look Forward to Seeing You

Laurelhurst Family Dentistry is conveniently located in the Laurelhurst community of Seattle, WA, and serves the University District, Fremont, and surrounding communities. To learn how you can achieve exceptional oral health and a beautiful, confident smile, simply call our office or request an appointment online!
